message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with spatial coherence and dereverberation, which are related to sound and acoustics. Other likely categories could be cs.SI (signal processing), cs.SY (systems and control), cs.MM (multimedia), and cs.LG (machine learning), as the paper proposes novel estimators and evaluates them using signal-based quality measures and automatic speech recognition accuracy.
